propList.Name: allowDrop
propList.Description: Whether to allow dropping on the node

propList.Name: autoExpandParent
propList.Description: Whether to automatically expand a parent treeNode

propList.Name: blockNode
propList.Description: Whether treeNode fill remaining horizontal space

propList.Name: checkable
propList.Description: Add a Checkbox before the treeNodes

propList.Name: checkedKeys
propList.Description: (Controlled) Specifies the keys of the checked treeNodes (PS: When this specifies the key of a treeNode which is also a parent treeNode, all the children treeNodes of will be checked; and vice versa, when it specifies the key of a treeNode which is a child treeNode, its parent treeNode will also be checked. When checkable and checkStrictly is true, its object has checked and halfChecked property. Regardless of whether the child or parent treeNode is checked, they won't impact each other

propList.Name: checkStrictly
propList.Description: Check treeNode precisely; parent treeNode and children treeNodes are not associated

propList.Name: defaultCheckedKeys
propList.Description: Specifies the keys of the default checked treeNodes

propList.Name: defaultExpandAll
propList.Description: Whether to expand all treeNodes by default

propList.Name: defaultExpandedKeys
propList.Description: Specify the keys of the default expanded treeNodes

propList.Name: defaultExpandParent
propList.Description: If auto expand parent treeNodes when init

propList.Name: defaultSelectedKeys
propList.Description: Specifies the keys of the default selected treeNodes

propList.Name: disabled
propList.Description: Whether disabled the tree

propList.Name: draggable
propList.Description: Specifies whether this Tree or the node is draggable (IE > 8)

propList.Name: expandedKeys
propList.Description: (Controlled) Specifies the keys of the expanded treeNodes

propList.Name: filterTreeNode
propList.Description: Defines a function to filter (highlight) treeNodes. When the function returns true, the corresponding treeNode will be highlighted

propList.Name: height
propList.Description: Config virtual scroll height. Will not support horizontal scroll when enable this

propList.Name: icon
propList.Description: Customize treeNode icon

propList.Name: loadData
propList.Description: Load data asynchronously

propList.Name: loadedKeys
propList.Description: (Controlled) Set loaded tree nodes. Need work with loadData

propList.Name: multiple
propList.Description: Allows selecting multiple treeNodes

propList.Name: selectable
propList.Description: Whether can be selected

propList.Name: selectedKeys
propList.Description: (Controlled) Specifies the keys of the selected treeNodes

propList.Name: showIcon
propList.Description: Shows the icon before a TreeNode's title. There is no default style; you must set a custom style for it if set to true

propList.Name: showLine
propList.Description: Shows a connecting line

propList.Name: switcherIcon
propList.Description: Customize collapse/expand icon of tree node

propList.Name: titleRender
propList.Description: Customize tree node title render

propList.Name: treeData
propList.Description: The treeNodes data Array, if set it then you need not to construct children TreeNode. (key should be unique across the whole array)

propList.Name: treeLoadedKeys
propList.Description: (Controlled) Set loaded tree nodes, work with loadData only

propList.Name: virtual
propList.Description: Disable virtual scroll when set to false

propList.Name: onCheck
propList.Description: Callback function for when the onCheck event occurs
propList.Type: function(checkedKeys, e:{checked: bool, checkedNodes, node, event, halfCheckedKeys})

propList.Name: onDragEnd
propList.Description: Callback function for when the onDragEnd event occurs

propList.Name: onDragEnter
propList.Description: Callback function for when the onDragEnter event occurs

propList.Name: onDragLeave
propList.Description: Callback function for when the onDragLeave event occurs

propList.Name: onDragOver
propList.Description: Callback function for when the onDragOver event occurs

propList.Name: onDragStart
propList.Description: Callback function for when the onDragStart event occurs

propList.Name: onDrop
propList.Description: Callback function for when the onDrop event occurs

propList.Name: onExpand
propList.Description: Callback function for when a treeNode is expanded or collapsed

propList.Name: onLoad
propList.Description: Callback function for when a treeNode is loaded

propList.Name: onRightClick
propList.Description: Callback function for when the user right clicks a treeNode

propList.Name: onSelect
propList.Description: Callback function for when the user clicks a treeNode
propList.Type: function(selectedKeys, e:{selected: bool, selectedNodes, node, event})
